summary:
...KRISTY FORECAST TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW ON SUNDAY...
 As of 2:00 PM PDT Sat Oct 26
 the center of Kristy was located near 20.7, -129.2
 with movement NW at 14 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 993 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
